right sided instead of 6NT on the bidding.  I imagine that usually
there won't be much positional advantage, and if there is, it will be
about equal between 6S and 6NT.  Although 6S rates to make more often
than 6NT (and 7S more often than 7NT), I don't estimate the extra
chances you can expect in 6S are enough to offset the extra 10 points
at matchpoints.  It is at IMPs where I expect 6S to be truly superior.

